{
  "title": "dali u mudal",
  "titleCh": "雨下的日子",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "憶起從前在愛蘭清苦的寫照，點點滴滴地重現，體會農夫的生活辛苦，使全家能夠一起生活快樂幸福，活在當下知足常樂。",
      "ab": "palalēng kaidi Auran a rētēl ka maxaluak. inih maxariak ki maxalēkat ohoda lia, tau umamah a saw awnu riak a mēkēn sumay liaka tubuxibux di mukukusa lia, karum xumak a saw ka papasukubi hawyayakēn lia! yamin mukalawas riak a lama, malēkēd ki mabaza ka mahatahatan.",
